	(6506, 'facebook134117896601221_1095715167108151', 'Guardian football', 'https://graph.facebook.com/134117896601221/picture?type=normal', 'facebook', 'https://www.facebook.com/134117896601221/posts/1095715167108151', 'https://graph.facebook.com/1095715167108151/picture?type=normal', 'Mr Mourinho asked me about a tackle, an offside and a goal-line clearance. I gave him brief answers to his questions. After this I asked him to leave the dressing room area. He refused. I asked him again. After he refused again I asked Mr Sutton to escort him from the room. At this point Mr Mourinho became very aggressive and animated. He shouted that you fucking referees are weak … [Arsène] Wenger is right about you … you are fucking weak', '', 'en', 'Mr Mourinho asked me about a tackle, an offside and a goal-line clearance. I gave him brief answers to his questions. After this I asked him to leave the dressing room area. He refused. I asked him again. After he refused again I asked Mr Sutton to escort him from the room. At this point Mr Mourinho became very aggressive and animated. He shouted that you fucking referees are weak … [Arsène] Wenger is right about you … you are fucking weak <a href=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/nov/06/jose-mourinho-stadium-ban-chelsea-fa-reasons>http://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/nov/06/jose-mourinho-stadium-ban-chelsea-fa-reasons</a>', '2015-11-06 17:38:15', 225),
